      "author": "ChrisH2 (Chris)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello All,</p>\n<p>I need to create a report that is across columns:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/2/f2c70aaa5dd962ca894158a6cbf0b9118e3d2168.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/2/f2c70aaa5dd962ca894158a6cbf0b9118e3d2168_2_690x101.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"101\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1597×234 26.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Each column is a numbers column and I need to create a bar chart that shows all of the columns total hours over a time periods. It seems like an easy thing to do, obviously, I can do it in excel but I would like to do it natively.</p>\n<p>Any ideas?</p>"
    },
