      "createdAt": "2024-07-31T18:46:55.879Z",
      "author": "Valeriia.H (Valeriia)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/supreme\">@supreme</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nWelcome to the community!</p>\n<p>To see how long each each phase tasks try <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000106?utm_source=Monday&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=Comment_reporting-across-columns_20240717\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Time in Status </a>app which helps to track time the Item has spent in each workflow status easily. So you can monitor how fast the Item moves between statuses.<br />\nYou’ll get user-friendly data on the board in a few seconds.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/9/b9fa33072428815ef1af97bdf9d6b7464a40008f.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/9/b9fa33072428815ef1af97bdf9d6b7464a40008f_2_690x175.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48\" width=\"690\" height=\"175\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×488 50.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>With our app you can easily manage Work Calendars to track just the time it takes during business hours</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/7/6783a9d8b7beba76f5f51539d92e8ba2556e68db.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 11.21.08\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/7/6783a9d8b7beba76f5f51539d92e8ba2556e68db_2_690x317.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 11.21.08\" width=\"690\" height=\"317\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 11.21.08</span><span class=\"informations\">1204×554 26.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Also you will be able to track how much time your issue spends in each status and much more by generating:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503882\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Time in Status Report</strong> </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503937\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Status Count Report</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503992/Transition+Count+Report.\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Transition Count Report</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/chart_with_upwards_trend.png?v=12\" title=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> And use <a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795504246\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>charts</strong></a> to visualize your reports a sample of a certain number according to time range/item range, or a <a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795504311\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>single</strong> </a><strong>item</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pie Charts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Bar Charts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Area Charts</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/3/03417e74cf9ef4149d165c89a2d96db3a532b3d4.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 09.29.46\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/3/03417e74cf9ef4149d165c89a2d96db3a532b3d4_2_330x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 09.29.46\" width=\"330\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 09.29.46</span><span class=\"informations\">954×1444 51.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>The app is also available in the format of board integration.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/7/e7392b1cf0f1d5828cc0b51ef89ca6a1de85d676.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/7/e7392b1cf0f1d5828cc0b51ef89ca6a1de85d676_2_690x284.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01\" width=\"690\" height=\"284\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01</span><span class=\"informations\">1538×634 95.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000106?utm_source=Monday&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=Comment_reporting-across-columns_20240717\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Start the 14-days free trial </a> to try it out for yourself and share your experience with us.</p>\n<p>Hope you find this app helpful,<br />\nValeriia</p>"
